 ed="R113" n="0936a02"/><head>迴首</head><lb
 ed="X" n="0783a12"/><lb
 ed="R113" n="0936a03"/><ab type="verse">轉腦旋蹄錯路頭何分頑劣與剛柔　　<lb
 ed="X" n="0783a13"/><lb
